<td>Write individually</td>
<td>Template formula + review</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Meta descriptions</td>
<td>Write individually</td>
<td>Generate from content + review</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Internal links</td>
<td>Search manually</td>
<td>Tool suggestions + approval</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Image alt text</td>
